Jon Weigel
Chief Executive John oversees the implementation of ODEKA’s community programs in Kananga. He works closely with local communities and international partners to coordinate all field operations.
His work has significantly improved the reach and efficiency of ODEKA’s educational and health initiatives across the Kasai region.
